text: Hubert Andrzej Olejnik (born 15 April 1982) is a Slovak sport shooter. He participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a medal.Double trap results ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1982 births Category:Slovak male sport shooters Category:Polish male sport shooters Category:Trap and double trap shooters Category:Sportspeople from Wrocław Category:Slovak people of Polish descent Category:Shooters at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Slovakia
